All Implemented Interfaces:
TestContext
public class LoveHateTester
extends InputOutputTest
implements TestContext

This class implements everything needed to create 'Loves' and 'Hates' reference test suites within the general testing framework.

This class extends the InputOutputTest class to represent a single Love/Hate test.

This class also implements the TestContext interface to be used by these tests.

Author:
R. James Firby
